Zendesk CommonUI SDK for iOS

Zendesk CommonUI SDK for mobile. The CommonUI SDK is a shared library among the Zendesk product SDKs. It is used to shared core UI components among our product SDKs.

Documentation

You can find our documentation on https://developer.zendesk.com/embeddables.

Feature requests and issues

All feature requests and issues are welcomed. Please see our contributing guidelines to find out how to contact us.
